# Telegram Bot Project

This project is a Telegram bot designed for managing and selling books and theater shows. Users can easily browse, search, and order products using interactive buttons and commands.  

## Features

- Supports two main categories:
  - ğŸ“š E-Books
  - Theaters
- View products, daily/monthly reports, and contact the admin
- Add documents and photos (admin only)
- Search by title or author
- Interactive buttons for selecting quantity, purchasing, and navigating products

## Commands

- `/start` : Show information buttons and main menu
- `/help` : Display all available commands
- `/document` : Instructions for adding a file (admin only)
- `/add_photo` : Instructions for adding a photo (admin only)

## Buttons

- ğŸ›ï¸ Products : Display product categories
- ğŸ“Š Daily / Monthly Report : User report (admin only)
- â˜ï¸ Contact Us : Contact information
- Coming soon! : Features under development

## How to Run

1. Install required packages:
```bash
pip install pyTelegramBotAPI




